{
  "text": "In this paper we relax condition [CITATION_1] and replace assumption (A2) with either (A2 ) (p, q) \u2192 P av (p, q; I) has an elliptic equilibrium in the origin p = q = 0 and the first order Birkhoff invariants are non resonant up to order four, i.e. , they verify (8) with 6 replaced by 4. or",
